<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 22:06:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚伊尔·戈兰能否利用他的英雄形象打造一个“新鲜、令人兴奋”的以色列左翼？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/can-yair-golan-leverage-his-hero-image-to-build-a-fresh-exciting-israeli-left/0000018c-456c-d6bd-a1ad-7ffe83fd0000</link><description>这位前将军在 10 月 7 日表现出的英雄主义改变了他的公众形象。现在，他面临着将新获得的人气转化为选票的挑战。在一次深度采访中，戈兰解释了他对加沙战争、与巴勒斯坦人的冲突以及作为以色列左派的态度</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 21:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/can-yair-golan-leverage-his-hero-image-to-build-a-fresh-exciting-israeli-left/0000018c-456c-d6bd-a1ad-7ffe83fd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府允许紧急使用私人安全摄像头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-okays-emergency-access-to-private-security-cams/0000018c-454a-dc19-a3ae-dfee3eaa0000</link><description>新法律允许以色列军队和安全部门在所有者不知情的情况下使用私人安全摄像头。立法者解释说，这是防止敌对摄像头窃听的必要条件，对国家安全至关重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-okays-emergency-access-to-private-security-cams/0000018c-454a-dc19-a3ae-dfee3eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>过去24小时内，五名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-last-24-hours-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-456a-dc19-a3ae-dfeefca00000</link><description>以色列军队首先宣布了周三被杀的三名以色列士兵的死亡，随后又公布了周四被杀的另外两名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 19:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-last-24-hours-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-456a-dc19-a3ae-dfeefca00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人悼念在加沙战斗中丧生的战时内阁部长、前以色列国防军司令加迪·艾森科特的儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-eulogize-son-of-war-cabinet-minister-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-4533-db03-a7dd-ed77e76c0000</link><description>艾森科特当时正在视察在加沙执行任务的第 162 师，此时他收到了 25 岁的儿子加尔战死的消息。内塔尼亚胡表示哀悼，称“他是一位勇敢的战士和真正的英雄”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 18:11:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-eulogize-son-of-war-cabinet-minister-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-4533-db03-a7dd-ed77e76c0000</guid></item><item><title>很快，拜登将呼吁结束战争。内塔尼亚胡会攻击他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-07/ty-article/.highlight/soon-biden-will-call-for-the-war-to-end-and-netanyahu-will-attack-him/0000018c-453a-db23-ad9f-6dfaba8b0000</link><description>那么，拜登唯一的问题是，他想在 2024 年什么时候与内塔尼亚胡进行一场战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-07/ty-article/.highlight/soon-biden-will-call-for-the-war-to-end-and-netanyahu-will-attack-him/0000018c-453a-db23-ad9f-6dfaba8b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于人质家人深陷繁文缛节，以色列未能设立机构来帮助他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/as-hostages-families-drown-in-red-tape-israel-fails-to-set-up-agency-to-help-them/0000018c-44de-db03-a7dd-eddf26600000</link><description>人质家属代表表示，有些家庭支离破碎，得不到任何支持，他们无法坚持下去。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/as-hostages-families-drown-in-red-tape-israel-fails-to-set-up-agency-to-help-them/0000018c-44de-db03-a7dd-eddf26600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方试图阻止主要由阿拉伯人组成的左翼哈达什党代表大会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-tries-to-prevent-left-wing-largely-arab-hadash-party-convention/0000018c-4513-d6bd-a1ad-7fd74a250000</link><description>以色列警方声称大会将包括煽动性言论，并威胁举办活动的设施所有者。哈达什领导人表示，议程将包括规划“反对战争继续和政治迫害的政治行动”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-tries-to-prevent-left-wing-largely-arab-hadash-party-convention/0000018c-4513-d6bd-a1ad-7fd74a250000</guid></item><item><title>泰国人在加沙被哈马斯扣为人质：以色列人“受到特别残酷的待遇”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/thai-man-held-hostage-in-gaza-recalls-beatings-and-bleakness/0000018c-444b-db23-ad9f-6cdb776b0000</link><description>阿努查·安卡尤 (Anucha Angkaew) 与其他几名以色列和泰国人质一起被哈马斯囚禁了 50 天。绑架者对他们拳打脚踢了两天。此后，他们又坚持对以色列人进行两天的殴打，用电线鞭打以色列人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 16:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/thai-man-held-hostage-in-gaza-recalls-beatings-and-bleakness/0000018c-444b-db23-ad9f-6cdb776b0000</guid></item><item><title>比利时禁止以色列定居者在西岸实施反巴勒斯坦暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</link><description>比利时总理效仿了拜登最近的制裁措施，并表示将推动欧盟效仿。他警告称，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，西岸定居者的暴力行为已达到历史最高水平，“针对平民的暴力行为将会产生后果”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</guid></item><item><title>“好犹太人”与“坏犹太人”：为什么支持巴勒斯坦的抗议活动有问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</link><description>我一直抗议以色列的占领和系统性的反阿拉伯歧视，但我不会加入纽约的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动。我永远不会接受有毒测试，要求我谴责其他犹太人，也不会与任何将杀害以色列人视为“抵抗”合法化的人一起游行</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</guid></item><item><title>来自耶路撒冷的信：战时我的家人、我的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/letter-from-jerusalem-my-family-my-country-at-wartime/0000018c-4394-db23-ad9f-6bdc67490000</link><description>10 月 7 日，我们从露营之旅中醒来，听到爆炸声。战争的恐怖开始显现：不仅是哈马斯的火箭弹，而且我们意识到我们的表弟也是从以色列被绑架到加沙的人之一。他什么时候回家？</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/letter-from-jerusalem-my-family-my-country-at-wartime/0000018c-4394-db23-ad9f-6bdc67490000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和常春藤盟校之间的美好友谊结束了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-beautiful-friendship-between-jews-and-the-ivy-league-is-over/0000018c-44cd-db23-ad9f-6cdd58760000</link><description>加沙战争加剧了这一趋势，但它早在几年前就开始了：常春藤盟校背弃了犹太人。现在犹太校友正在回报我们</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-beautiful-friendship-between-jews-and-the-ivy-league-is-over/0000018c-44cd-db23-ad9f-6cdd58760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部长为内塔尼亚胡之子亚伊尔和党员下令发​​放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-orders-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-party-members-son/0000018c-4472-db23-ad9f-6cfadeee0000</link><description>外交部专业工作人员认为发放护照不合适，但外交部长伊莱·科恩绕过了他们。一位熟悉外交部门的消息人士表示，“这味道特别难闻”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:06:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-orders-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-party-members-son/0000018c-4472-db23-ad9f-6cfadeee0000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的以色列人质的漫长康复之路才刚刚开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-long-road-to-recovery-for-freed-israeli-hostages-has-only-just-begun/0000018c-3f62-d6a5-afae-bf72c4b20000</link><description>以色列从未面临过如此规模的重建项目。很难预测人质的完全康复之路将如何结束，甚至是否结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/the-long-road-to-recovery-for-freed-israeli-hostages-has-only-just-begun/0000018c-3f62-d6a5-afae-bf72c4b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡，无视美国关于加沙的想法，后果自负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignore-the-u-s-ideas-about-gaza-at-your-peril/0000018c-43f0-d2d5-abef-f7f72feb0000</link><description>在华盛顿，人们认识到以色列与哈马斯的战争不符合或源于任何政治目标。因此，两个月后，美国人单方面提出了自己的框架，尽管他们知道极端主义的内塔尼亚胡政府永远不会同意。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 14:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignore-the-u-s-ideas-about-gaza-at-your-peril/0000018c-43f0-d2d5-abef-f7f72feb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵宣称加沙北部建筑是查巴德之家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-proclaim-a-chabad-house-in-northern-gaza-damaged-building/0000018c-43a1-db23-ad9f-6bf9bd320000</link><description>这个想法似乎来自一些在特拉维夫学习的美国犹太学院学生，他们计划在南下时张贴更多标志。查巴德运动的已故领导人坚信以色列必须保留对以色列所有圣经土地的控制权</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 13:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-proclaim-a-chabad-house-in-northern-gaza-damaged-building/0000018c-43a1-db23-ad9f-6bf9bd320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵记录在西岸射杀巴勒斯坦残疾人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-documented-shooting-a-palestinian-with-special-needs-in-west-bank/0000018c-4411-d2d5-abef-f5771f430000</link><description>34 岁的塔里克·阿布·阿贝德 (Tariq Abu &amp;#39;Abed) 在希伯伦下班回家时，士兵拦住了他，要求他出示身份证件。没有它，他们就用枪指着他。当他做出解释的手势时，他们开枪打死了他。他的母亲与《国土报》分享了他的账户</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 12:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-documented-shooting-a-palestinian-with-special-needs-in-west-bank/0000018c-4411-d2d5-abef-f5771f430000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺游行期间警察与极右翼犹太民族主义者发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-activists-to-rally-in-jerusalems-old-city-for-full-control-over-temple-mount/0000018c-4414-d89c-a3ef-4e3762e30000</link><description>极右活动人士在耶路撒冷老城的穆斯林区游行，呼吁“犹太人完全控制”圣殿山/阿克萨大院，并进行种族主义辱骂</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 12:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-activists-to-rally-in-jerusalems-old-city-for-full-control-over-temple-mount/0000018c-4414-d89c-a3ef-4e3762e30000</guid></item><item><title>由于几乎没有互联网接入和令人困惑的以色列国防军推文，加沙人不知道该去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-hardly-any-internet-access-and-confusing-idf-tweets-gazans-dont-know-where-to-go/0000018c-3e7b-d53d-a7fc-beff3f3e0000</link><description>以色列国防军的阿拉伯语发言人发布了一张难以理解的地图，上面有乱码的地名，加沙人将用它来做出生死攸关的决定；人权组织报告称，地图上的避难所已经因人潮拥挤和必需品缺乏而崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 11:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-hardly-any-internet-access-and-confusing-idf-tweets-gazans-dont-know-where-to-go/0000018c-3e7b-d53d-a7fc-beff3f3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长下令不经审判就拘留被指控袭击巴勒斯坦人的定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-orders-settler-accused-of-palestinians-assault-held-without-trial/0000018c-3f85-d2e7-ab8d-bff518cb0000</link><description>随着美国打击针对约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为的压力越来越大，约阿夫·加兰特签署了针对塔尔·伊农·达迪克的命令。极右翼部长本-格维尔暗示国防部长“很困惑，忘记了朋友和敌人的区别”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 11:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-minister-orders-settler-accused-of-palestinians-assault-held-without-trial/0000018c-3f85-d2e7-ab8d-bff518cb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>